sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: User API Request with Kubernetes RBAC

    Client->>Proxy: HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token (SA/OIDC)
    Proxy->>MLflow: HTTP/5000 (pod-local)<br/>x-remote-user + x-remote-groups headers
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: allowed: true/false
    MLflow->>PG: SQL Query<br/>TCP/5432 TLS 1.2+<br/>Username/Password
    PG-->>MLflow: Query Results
    MLflow->>S3: GET/PUT Artifact<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>AWS Credentials
    S3-->>MLflow: Artifact Data
    MLflow-->>Proxy: JSON Response
    Proxy-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: AI Gateway LLM Proxy

    participant LLM as LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Client->>Proxy: POST /gateway/openai/v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token
    Proxy->>MLflow: HTTP/5000<br/>x-remote-user headers
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(gatewayendpoints/use)
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: allowed: true
    MLflow->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>API Key (from DB)
    LLM-->>MLflow: Streaming Response
    MLflow-->>Proxy: Streaming Response
    Proxy-->>Client: HTTPS Streaming Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Module Federation UI Embedding

    participant Dashboard as OpenShift AI Dashboard
    participant Browser as User Browser

    Browser->>Dashboard: Load Dashboard Page
    Dashboard-->>Browser: HTML with Federation Config
    Browser->>Proxy: GET /static-files/federated/remoteEntry.js<br/>HTTPS/443
    Proxy->>MLflow: HTTP/5000
    MLflow-->>Proxy: remoteEntry.js
    Proxy-->>Browser: JS Module
    Browser->>Proxy: AJAX API calls<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    Proxy->>MLflow: HTTP/5000<br/>x-remote-user headers
    MLflow-->>Proxy: JSON Data
    Proxy-->>Browser: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: OTLP Trace Ingestion

    participant SDK as ML Workload (SDK)

    SDK->>Proxy: POST /v1/traces<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token
    Proxy->>MLflow: HTTP/5000<br/>x-remote-user headers
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(experiments update)
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: allowed: true
    MLflow->>PG: Store Trace/Spans<br/>TCP/5432 TLS 1.2+
    PG-->>MLflow: OK
    MLflow-->>Proxy: 200 OK
    Proxy-->>SDK: HTTPS 200 OK
